data.name: sqlDataSource1.SelectCommand
data.value:
SELECT rca.id, rca.name, rca.description, rca.analysis_file, employee.alpha_name, rca.start_date, rca.completion_date, lead.leader,facilitator.facilitator FROM rca LEFT OUTER JOIN rca_team_connector ON rca.id_team = rca_team_connector.id JOIN users on rca_team_connector.id_user = users.username JOIN employee on users.employee_id = employee.id left outer join
(SELECT rca_team_connector.id_rca, employee.alpha_name as leader from rca_team_connector join users on rca_team_connector.id_user = users.username join employee on users.employee_id = employee.id where rca_team_connector.rca_position = 1) as lead on rca.id = lead.id_rca left outer join
(SELECT rca_team_connector.id_rca, employee.alpha_name as facilitator from rca_team_connector join users on rca_team_connector.id_user = users.username join employee on users.employee_id = employee.id where rca_team_connector.rca_position = 3) as facilitator on rca.id = facilitator.id_rca
